## Budget / stop

These limits are **hard stops**, not suggestions. When any limit is reached,
the loop halts immediately, writes a `budget-exceeded` status to `{{STATE_PATH}}`,
and waits for a human to either raise the budget or mark the loop done.

| Dimension | Limit | Action on breach |
|-----------|-------|-----------------|
| Max iterations | _(set at scaffold time)_ | Halt + write budget-exceeded |
| Token / API cost cap | _(set at scaffold time)_ | Halt + write budget-exceeded |
| Wall-clock time cap | _(set at scaffold time)_ | Halt + write budget-exceeded |

